Package: epicoda
Type: Package
Title: Supports epidemiological analyses using compositional exposure variables
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: person("Rosemary", "Walmsley", email = "rosemary.walmsley@gtc.ox.ac.uk",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: <rosemary.walmsley@gtc.ox.ac.uk>
Description: Provides functions to support epidemiological analyses using compositional 
    exposure variables, including preparation of ilr-pivot coordinates and plotting 
    graphs of model predictions for linear, logistic and Cox regression models.  
